[
  {
    "text": "*Gasp*",
    "start": 10.833,
    "duration": 1.754
  },
  {
    "text": "Where??",
    "start": 15.201,
    "duration": 0.816
  },
  {
    "text": "Someone licked the frosting off the cupcakes-",
    "start": 16.245,
    "duration": 2.459
  },
  {
    "text": "and now they're just UGLY MUFFINS!",
    "start": 18.704,
    "duration": 1.764
  },
  {
    "text": "*Groupd gasp*",
    "start": 20.468,
    "duration": 1.052
  },
  {
    "text": "Who would do such a thing?!",
    "start": 21.52,
    "duration": 1.759
  },
  {
    "text": "Judah",
    "start": 24.436,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you still gonna eat that?",
    "start": 25.524,
    "duration": 2.042
  },
  {
    "text": "Nooooo",
    "start": 28.72,
    "duration": 2.552
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay! Is anybody sus?",
    "start": 31.272,
    "duration": 2.293
  },
  {
    "text": "Red's sus!!",
    "start": 35.12,
    "duration": 1.377
  },
  {
    "text": "Now you guys won't believe me at first but--",
    "start": 36.497,
    "duration": 1.343
  },
  {
    "text": "wait what?",
    "start": 38.64,
    "duration": 0.918
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah I agree.",
    "start": 39.558,
    "duration": 1.164
  },
  {
    "text": "Red is sus.",
    "start": 40.722,
    "duration": 1.318
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah she's been imposter like 50 percent of the time!!",
    "start": 42.04,
    "duration": 2.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Haha!!",
    "start": 46.304,
    "duration": 1.242
  },
  {
    "text": "Britney...",
    "start": 49.52,
    "duration": 2.068
  },
  {
    "text": "was...",
    "start": 51.588,
    "duration": 1.215
  },
  {
    "text": "The imposter?",
    "start": 53.675,
    "duration": 1.391
  },
  {
    "text": "yeah!!!",
    "start": 55.066,
    "duration": 0.879
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh yeah!!!",
    "start": 55.945,
    "duration": 0.879
  },
  {
    "text": "We were actually right??",
    "start": 56.824,
    "duration": 1.956
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh yeah!!!",
    "start": 58.78,
    "duration": 1.22
  },
  {
    "text": "YEAHH!! WHOOOOO!!!",
    "start": 60.0,
    "duration": 1.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Mom gave us each a list of tasks to \ndo what we're boat sitting the cruise ship, again!  ",
    "start": 61.92,
    "duration": 3.4
  },
  {
    "text": "So get 'em done!",
    "start": 65.32,
    "duration": 0.92
  },
  {
    "text": "And remember there were three imposters but now they're only two!",
    "start": 66.24,
    "duration": 2.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah!!",
    "start": 69.661,
    "duration": 0.995
  },
  {
    "text": "Judah.",
    "start": 72.902,
    "duration": 0.881
  },
  {
    "text": "Put the muffin back.",
    "start": 73.783,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait. I don't have any tasks up here why'd I come upstairs?",
    "start": 83.945,
    "duration": 2.554
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey hey! Mary's leaving! That's sus!",
    "start": 86.499,
    "duration": 2.158
  },
  {
    "text": "That's sus!!",
    "start": 88.657,
    "duration": 1.114
  },
  {
    "text": "No!! I forgot where my tasks were!!",
    "start": 89.771,
    "duration": 2.249
  },
  {
    "text": "That's sus!! That's sus!!",
    "start": 92.02,
    "duration": 1.247
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh hey what's that?",
    "start": 95.2,
    "duration": 1.066
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah this book I got.",
    "start": 96.266,
    "duration": 1.026
  },
  {
    "text": "How to be a better crewmate.",
    "start": 97.292,
    "duration": 1.447
  },
  {
    "text": "Step one!",
    "start": 98.739,
    "duration": 1.069
  },
  {
    "text": "Red is sus. ",
    "start": 99.808,
    "duration": 1.306
  },
  {
    "text": "I knew it!",
    "start": 101.114,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Greatest crewmates! We're the greatest crew-",
    "start": 103.171,
    "duration": 3.229
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait wait wait Jocelyn!",
    "start": 106.4,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "We can't sing that! We're not crewmates",
    "start": 107.68,
    "duration": 1.555
  },
  {
    "text": "We're the imposter!!",
    "start": 109.235,
    "duration": 0.987
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh!",
    "start": 111.018,
    "duration": 0.995
  },
  {
    "text": "We're the greatest imposter!! We're the greatest imposter!! ",
    "start": 112.924,
    "duration": 5.526
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay. Glue back the ancient vase.",
    "start": 119.52,
    "duration": 2.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't sneeze.",
    "start": 126.24,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "We're the greatest impoooster ",
    "start": 131.034,
    "duration": 2.873
  },
  {
    "text": "What did she just say?",
    "start": 134.64,
    "duration": 1.513
  },
  {
    "text": "Nothing!",
    "start": 136.153,
    "duration": 0.885
  },
  {
    "text": "Kids say the uh...",
    "start": 137.038,
    "duration": 1.151
  },
  {
    "text": "strangest things.",
    "start": 138.189,
    "duration": 1.925
  },
  {
    "text": "Hmm",
    "start": 140.228,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Can we get him now?",
    "start": 143.136,
    "duration": 1.984
  },
  {
    "text": "No Jocelyn we have to do this smartly!",
    "start": 145.12,
    "duration": 2.473
  },
  {
    "text": "Could we get him smartly?",
    "start": 147.593,
    "duration": 3.412
  },
  {
    "text": "okay!",
    "start": 151.384,
    "duration": 0.831
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah! What is it?",
    "start": 155.0,
    "duration": 0.792
  },
  {
    "text": "My task is to clean the boys bathroom!",
    "start": 155.912,
    "duration": 2.651
  },
  {
    "text": "I am so sorry...",
    "start": 159.736,
    "duration": 1.604
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you.",
    "start": 161.34,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "*inhales*",
    "start": 162.93,
    "duration": 1.033
  },
  {
    "text": "Left! Right!",
    "start": 163.963,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Left! Right!",
    "start": 165.963,
    "duration": 1.477
  },
  {
    "text": "Stop!",
    "start": 167.44,
    "duration": 0.786
  },
  {
    "text": "The lights??",
    "start": 168.226,
    "duration": 2.175
  },
  {
    "text": "Turn them off and get the people.",
    "start": 170.401,
    "duration": 3.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Sabotage lights and throw out the \npeople who come to fix it??",
    "start": 173.92,
    "duration": 2.17
  },
  {
    "text": "I like it!!",
    "start": 176.735,
    "duration": 1.409
  },
  {
    "text": "Mhmm!!",
    "start": 178.144,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Ohh lights are out!!",
    "start": 182.64,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh no.",
    "start": 188.08,
    "duration": 1.021
  },
  {
    "text": "Decided to join me, huh?",
    "start": 194.08,
    "duration": 2.257
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm going back in the water. ",
    "start": 196.337,
    "duration": 2.091
  },
  {
    "text": "Lights are out!",
    "start": 198.428,
    "duration": 1.735
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh.",
    "start": 200.163,
    "duration": 0.824
  },
  {
    "text": " We got them! Now we vent!!",
    "start": 202.637,
    "duration": 2.363
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm the leader, I say when we vent.",
    "start": 205.36,
    "duration": 3.437
  },
  {
    "text": "Now we vent!",
    "start": 209.252,
    "duration": 1.773
  },
  {
    "text": "*gasp*",
    "start": 214.547,
    "duration": 0.976
  },
  {
    "text": "Where??",
    "start": 217.729,
    "duration": 0.911
  },
  {
    "text": "Someone left the milk out",
    "start": 218.64,
    "duration": 1.815
  },
  {
    "text": "and now it's room temperature!",
    "start": 220.455,
    "duration": 2.105
  },
  {
    "text": "*group gasp*",
    "start": 222.56,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "And someone got Daniel!",
    "start": 224.4,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "*Group gasp*",
    "start": 225.768,
    "duration": 1.422
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait a second I didn't do either of those things....",
    "start": 227.19,
    "duration": 2.316
  },
  {
    "text": "'cause I'm an innocent crewmate.",
    "start": 230.72,
    "duration": 3.681
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh look someone got Judah out oh no.\n*Group gasp*",
    "start": 235.462,
    "duration": 2.855
  },
  {
    "text": "Daniel?",
    "start": 238.317,
    "duration": 1.223
  },
  {
    "text": "AH!",
    "start": 239.54,
    "duration": 0.904
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay does anybody know who the imposter is?",
    "start": 241.108,
    "duration": 1.941
  },
  {
    "text": "yeah",
    "start": 243.352,
    "duration": 0.908
  },
  {
    "text": "Jessica is the imposter!",
    "start": 244.26,
    "duration": 2.774
  },
  {
    "text": "What why??",
    "start": 247.28,
    "duration": 1.39
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, why should we believe you?",
    "start": 248.67,
    "duration": 1.943
  },
  {
    "text": "'Cause I am so cute!",
    "start": 250.973,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "Awww",
    "start": 253.101,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah. I mean she is a pretty cute baby.",
    "start": 253.601,
    "duration": 2.847
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll vote for that!",
    "start": 256.448,
    "duration": 0.916
  },
  {
    "text": "No guys!",
    "start": 257.364,
    "duration": 0.866
  },
  {
    "text": "Jocelyn's been acting super sus.",
    "start": 258.23,
    "duration": 1.514
  },
  {
    "text": "I think it's her and Micah.",
    "start": 259.744,
    "duration": 1.173
  },
  {
    "text": "*Cries*",
    "start": 262.413,
    "duration": 1.298
  },
  {
    "text": "Awwwww",
    "start": 264.621,
    "duration": 1.697
  },
  {
    "text": "No, no.",
    "start": 266.318,
    "duration": 1.532
  },
  {
    "text": "Please don't cry.",
    "start": 267.85,
    "duration": 0.742
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow good job Josiah.",
    "start": 268.592,
    "duration": 1.007
  },
  {
    "text": "You made a baby cry",
    "start": 269.599,
    "duration": 1.682
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay fine we can vote out Jessica.",
    "start": 271.6,
    "duration": 2.856
  },
  {
    "text": "Yaaayyy!",
    "start": 274.614,
    "duration": 1.485
  },
  {
    "text": "Ahhh ",
    "start": 278.183,
    "duration": 1.17
  },
  {
    "text": "Jessica...",
    "start": 280.16,
    "duration": 1.086
  },
  {
    "text": "Was...",
    "start": 281.246,
    "duration": 1.008
  },
  {
    "text": "Not this imposter!",
    "start": 282.475,
    "duration": 1.37
  },
  {
    "text": "Aww man!!",
    "start": 283.845,
    "duration": 1.39
  },
  {
    "text": "Your cheese is dripping.",
    "start": 292.64,
    "duration": 1.592
  },
  {
    "text": "Yay we got Daniel!",
    "start": 294.701,
    "duration": 1.917
  },
  {
    "text": "No Jocelyn that wasn't us!",
    "start": 297.13,
    "duration": 1.469
  },
  {
    "text": "That was the other imposter!",
    "start": 298.721,
    "duration": 2.113
  },
  {
    "text": "They must be super good.",
    "start": 300.834,
    "duration": 2.501
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah really good.",
    "start": 303.335,
    "duration": 1.625
  },
  {
    "text": "It's all clear!",
    "start": 308.32,
    "duration": 1.225
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh hey, Josiah's safe.",
    "start": 334.32,
    "duration": 1.886
  },
  {
    "text": "I wonder what he's doing.",
    "start": 336.206,
    "duration": 1.634
  },
  {
    "text": "Not today imposter!",
    "start": 341.92,
    "duration": 1.374
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh I think he found something!",
    "start": 344.377,
    "duration": 1.396
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait up!! ",
    "start": 345.773,
    "duration": 1.085
  },
  {
    "text": "Ahhhhhhh",
    "start": 348.699,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Mary's the imposter??",
    "start": 353.84,
    "duration": 1.62
  },
  {
    "text": "No no no...",
    "start": 355.46,
    "duration": 1.497
  },
  {
    "text": "No she's just really sus.",
    "start": 356.957,
    "duration": 1.763
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
    "start": 358.72,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay Mary is the imposter.",
    "start": 363.84,
    "duration": 2.214
  },
  {
    "text": "She chased me around the whole ship",
    "start": 366.054,
    "duration": 1.518
  },
  {
    "text": "and I barely avoided her not throwing me off.",
    "start": 367.572,
    "duration": 2.02
  },
  {
    "text": "*Gasp*",
    "start": 369.592,
    "duration": 0.854
  },
  {
    "text": "Oooohhhh",
    "start": 371.903,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay so there's actually a really good \nreason for this...",
    "start": 375.12,
    "duration": 2.644
  },
  {
    "text": "okay!",
    "start": 381.601,
    "duration": 0.924
  },
  {
    "text": "Mary...",
    "start": 382.525,
    "duration": 0.705
  },
  {
    "text": "was...",
    "start": 383.23,
    "duration": 1.451
  },
  {
    "text": "NOT the imoster!",
    "start": 384.681,
    "duration": 1.283
  },
  {
    "text": "What was that??",
    "start": 390.4,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "I was investigating!!",
    "start": 391.6,
    "duration": 1.785
  },
  {
    "text": "Gosh it's like none of you have done this before!",
    "start": 394.192,
    "duration": 2.578
  },
  {
    "text": "Jocelyn what did you do?!",
    "start": 399.6,
    "duration": 1.486
  },
  {
    "text": "You're gonna overheat the engine and blow up the whole boat!!!",
    "start": 401.086,
    "duration": 2.194
  },
  {
    "text": "hehehe...",
    "start": 403.834,
    "duration": 1.459
  },
  {
    "text": "YESSS",
    "start": 405.293,
    "duration": 1.506
  },
  {
    "text": "Man being the imposter is not good for you.",
    "start": 407.36,
    "duration": 2.189
  },
  {
    "text": "oh",
    "start": 410.12,
    "duration": 1.038
  },
  {
    "text": "Elijah I think you dropped this.",
    "start": 411.158,
    "duration": 1.639
  },
  {
    "text": "oh that's weird",
    "start": 412.797,
    "duration": 1.373
  },
  {
    "text": "Uh oh...",
    "start": 415.28,
    "duration": 1.321
  },
  {
    "text": "okay okay!",
    "start": 418.067,
    "duration": 0.814
  },
  {
    "text": "Uhh",
    "start": 418.881,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't look sus! Don't look sus!",
    "start": 419.381,
    "duration": 1.921
  },
  {
    "text": "Do you know how to cool down the engine?",
    "start": 423.334,
    "duration": 1.467
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't know I'm not an engine doctor! ",
    "start": 424.801,
    "duration": 1.764
  },
  {
    "text": "Ahhhh",
    "start": 426.565,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Micah have you been here this whole time?",
    "start": 431.867,
    "duration": 2.104
  },
  {
    "text": "Nooo",
    "start": 435.0,
    "duration": 1.135
  },
  {
    "text": "I was just",
    "start": 436.135,
    "duration": 1.523
  },
  {
    "text": "innocently fixing the engine",
    "start": 437.658,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "Innocently..",
    "start": 440.058,
    "duration": 1.098
  },
  {
    "text": "woooow",
    "start": 443.2,
    "duration": 1.721
  },
  {
    "text": "I know it was Jocelyn and Micah!",
    "start": 449.293,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah! AND they were waiting by the engine for us!",
    "start": 451.629,
    "duration": 2.008
  },
  {
    "text": "And they've been acting super sus this whole time!",
    "start": 453.637,
    "duration": 2.412
  },
  {
    "text": "I will get you next!",
    "start": 456.995,
    "duration": 2.253
  },
  {
    "text": "*Slow gasp*",
    "start": 459.248,
    "duration": 1.263
  },
  {
    "text": "And by \"get you next\"",
    "start": 460.64,
    "duration": 2.258
  },
  {
    "text": "she means get you flowers! ",
    "start": 462.898,
    "duration": 2.535
  },
  {
    "text": "Next...",
    "start": 465.433,
    "duration": 1.054
  },
  {
    "text": "No!",
    "start": 466.487,
    "duration": 1.082
  },
  {
    "text": "I will throw you off the ship!",
    "start": 467.569,
    "duration": 3.06
  },
  {
    "text": "You know maybe it's best we take \na break from being the imposter?",
    "start": 471.92,
    "duration": 2.833
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay come on!",
    "start": 477.52,
    "duration": 1.229
  },
  {
    "text": "Micah was..",
    "start": 478.749,
    "duration": 2.306
  },
  {
    "text": "AN IMPOSTER!!!",
    "start": 481.055,
    "duration": 1.474
  },
  {
    "text": "YEAH!!",
    "start": 482.529,
    "duration": 1.051
  },
  {
    "text": "That's a lot of crime for a little baby.",
    "start": 483.58,
    "duration": 1.586
  },
  {
    "text": "yeah",
    "start": 485.166,
    "duration": 0.932
  },
  {
    "text": "Now remember guys there's still one impostor left!",
    "start": 486.61,
    "duration": 2.305
  },
  {
    "text": "right right",
    "start": 488.915,
    "duration": 1.468
  },
  {
    "text": "Mom said I had to come out here.",
    "start": 494.08,
    "duration": 3.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Why?",
    "start": 500.699,
    "duration": 0.581
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay! I think it's Kaylee!",
    "start": 501.28,
    "duration": 1.588
  },
  {
    "text": "Most often the new person is the imposter.",
    "start": 502.868,
    "duration": 1.811
  },
  {
    "text": "And the last three imposters have been girls!",
    "start": 504.679,
    "duration": 2.307
  },
  {
    "text": "What about Shiloh? She's a girl.",
    "start": 507.334,
    "duration": 2.134
  },
  {
    "text": "Shiloh's not a girl. Shiloh's our sister.",
    "start": 511.44,
    "duration": 2.069
  },
  {
    "text": "Pfft yeah.",
    "start": 513.509,
    "duration": 1.492
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay Kaylee!",
    "start": 515.001,
    "duration": 1.586
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you the imposter?",
    "start": 516.587,
    "duration": 0.933
  },
  {
    "text": "Noooo?",
    "start": 518.72,
    "duration": 1.549
  },
  {
    "text": "Why are you smiling?",
    "start": 520.86,
    "duration": 1.265
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't know why but when I'm accused I smile.",
    "start": 522.519,
    "duration": 3.809
  },
  {
    "text": "And it's becoming a real problem...",
    "start": 526.328,
    "duration": 2.576
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay.",
    "start": 529.486,
    "duration": 0.985
  },
  {
    "text": "If you're not imposter, stop smiling.",
    "start": 530.471,
    "duration": 2.444
  },
  {
    "text": "I can't...",
    "start": 532.915,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "All right.",
    "start": 538.8,
    "duration": 0.891
  },
  {
    "text": "Kaylee was...",
    "start": 539.691,
    "duration": 1.859
  },
  {
    "text": "NOT the imposter.",
    "start": 541.55,
    "duration": 2.382
  },
  {
    "text": "Guys that means it's one of us.",
    "start": 544.365,
    "duration": 2.254
  },
  {
    "text": "I only have a couple tasks left.",
    "start": 548.4,
    "duration": 1.738
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's finish them and end this!",
    "start": 550.138,
    "duration": 1.892
  },
  {
    "text": "That's right.",
    "start": 552.227,
    "duration": 1.422
  },
  {
    "text": "Why is it always down to three people?",
    "start": 554.08,
    "duration": 2.004
  },
  {
    "text": "Can't we win at four or five?",
    "start": 556.084,
    "duration": 1.828
  },
  {
    "text": "or even right off the top?",
    "start": 557.912,
    "duration": 1.545
  },
  {
    "text": "*gasp*",
    "start": 562.948,
    "duration": 0.956
  },
  {
    "text": "Josiah it's Elijah!",
    "start": 567.44,
    "duration": 1.111
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm positive!",
    "start": 568.551,
    "duration": 1.023
  },
  {
    "text": "What?? I've been doing my task this whole time!",
    "start": 569.574,
    "duration": 2.316
  },
  {
    "text": "I have a reason but it's gonna sound crazy!",
    "start": 571.89,
    "duration": 2.33
  },
  {
    "text": "Josiah you just have to believe me.",
    "start": 574.22,
    "duration": 2.036
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh snap.",
    "start": 576.847,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "It's her! Okay think about it!",
    "start": 578.182,
    "duration": 1.689
  },
  {
    "text": "we know this imposter is really good!",
    "start": 579.871,
    "duration": 1.705
  },
  {
    "text": "which means it can't be me it has to be her!",
    "start": 581.576,
    "duration": 1.759
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on Josiah!",
    "start": 583.985,
    "duration": 1.015
  },
  {
    "text": "You know the right call here!",
    "start": 585.0,
    "duration": 1.081
  },
  {
    "text": "It's Elijah it's him it's not me!",
    "start": 586.081,
    "duration": 2.436
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay at first I thought it was Shiloh.",
    "start": 588.517,
    "duration": 1.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Then Elijah and then Shiloh!",
    "start": 589.817,
    "duration": 1.657
  },
  {
    "text": "And I just don't know who it is!",
    "start": 591.474,
    "duration": 1.478
  },
  {
    "text": "oh come on!! Think about it!",
    "start": 592.952,
    "duration": 1.927
  },
  {
    "text": "Think about it. Its her!! You have to believe me!!",
    "start": 594.879,
    "duration": 2.343
  },
  {
    "text": "It's Elijah! Its her!!",
    "start": 597.222,
    "duration": 1.586
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on Josiah it's him!! It's not me!",
    "start": 598.808,
    "duration": 2.459
  },
  {
    "text": "okay..",
    "start": 601.267,
    "duration": 1.266
  },
  {
    "text": "Shiloh. I'm gonna trust you.",
    "start": 602.533,
    "duration": 1.452
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay okay!",
    "start": 608.801,
    "duration": 0.751
  },
  {
    "text": "Elijah was...",
    "start": 609.552,
    "duration": 2.006
  },
  {
    "text": "THE imposter!!!",
    "start": 611.558,
    "duration": 1.392
  },
  {
    "text": "YEAHH!!! Woooo!!",
    "start": 612.95,
    "duration": 1.69
  },
  {
    "text": "How'd you know?!",
    "start": 614.64,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "I saw his book had tape lines on it.",
    "start": 615.92,
    "duration": 2.251
  },
  {
    "text": "Which means the real title should be...",
    "start": 618.84,
    "duration": 2.469
  },
  {
    "text": "How to be a better imposter...",
    "start": 622.96,
    "duration": 1.891
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh that's good.",
    "start": 625.402,
    "duration": 1.309
  },
  {
    "text": "You three stink at imposters!",
    "start": 630.72,
    "duration": 2.813
  },
  {
    "text": "*arguing*",
    "start": 633.84,
    "duration": 6.88
  }
]